/**
 * Mock data for Finance · Month Close.
 *
 * The page is a stateful gate: 6 checklist items, of which the non-`soft`
 * blockers determine whether the month can close. Click a Bridge button
 * on a blocking item → it flips to done, the gate unlocks, the
 * close-readiness metric updates, and the final summary becomes exportable.
 */

